  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Drugs and pharmaceutical electronic market information tool (eMIT)
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The eMIT provides information about prices and usage for generic drugs and pharmaceutical products.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

