<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This tool gives background information on the pharmaceuticals that hospitals might buy.</p>

<p>The data provided includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>an estimate of NHS hospital-sector annual usage from English trusts for the product selected</li>
  <li>the average price paid for that product over the last 4 months of the period</li>
  <li>a measure of how much that average changed</li>
</ul>

<p>The data within the eMIT represents the 12-month period to the end of June 2018.</p>

</div>
</div>

